remarks: Closed form of ~ strcollnf .  Version of ~ ax-strcoll with one DV condition removed, the other DV condition replaced by a non-freeness antecedent, and without initial universal quantifier.  (Contributed by BJ, 21-Oct-2019.)
statement:
strcollnft $p |- ( A. x A. y F/ b ph -> ( A. x e. a E. y ph -> E. b A. y ( y e. b <-> E. x e. a ph ) ) ) $.
$d a b x y $.
